title: Pedestrian struck by vehicle, killed in St. Paul
text: Pedestrian struck by vehicle, killed in St. Paul The crash occurred at the intersection of Dayton Avenue and West Mississippi River Blvd. By Karen Zamora Star Tribune February 22, 2017 â€” 6:52pm Purchase: Order Reprint A pedestrian was struck by a vehicle and killed Wednesday evening in St. Paul.
